{"tid":2377112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"侵粉離散 陰謀論者搬龍門","createTime":"2021-01-23T10:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T12:51:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"71da47f8505cb865bcb95fff376d982b8746d60c","tid":2377112,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:26:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210123/XR365VSSGVAU3P2MPI6YYMAUVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210123%2FXR365VSSGVAU3P2MPI6YYMAUVE%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TahTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=221b5fef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210123%2FXR365VSSGVAU3P2MPI6YYMAUVE%2F&h=86276c60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210123/XR365VSSGVAU3P2MPI6YYMAUVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n侵粉離散 陰謀論者搬龍門<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lTGVgNBJ14M4lSo1JkH7_BSg-sI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HC5MNPUL7RDHLBUQCJDRX364XI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlTGVgNBJ14M4lSo1JkH7_BSg-sI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHC5MNPUL7RDHLBUQCJDRX364XI.jpg&h=575c8fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■紐約有路牌被塗鴉，把街名改成「特朗普已走街」，「單程」行車亦變「已離開」。<br />\n<br />\n美國前任總統特朗普周三乖乖下台，令支持他的極右團體和陰謀論社群開始重新洗牌，部份人開始揚棄特朗普和驚覺自己被騙了四年，但亦有人「搬龍門」修改預言信到底。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：行政聚焦抗疫 入境須隔離  稱援助將至 拜登迫令戴罩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n極右支持者斥反應軟弱<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在月初衝擊國會事件後，雖未跟暴力示威者完全割席，但也沒鼓勵他們進一步行動。「驕傲男孩」、「美國優先」、「守誓者」等極右組織的討論區和Telegram頻道，都有人批評他反應軟弱，甚至「一敗塗地」。<br />\n<br />\n陰謀論社群QAnon的信徒在周三拜登就職禮前深信，這天就是他們預言的「風暴」，特朗普將在軍方支持下反撲。預言最終沒成真，他們的先知「Q」亦至少44日沒發新訊息，部份追隨者說感到中了一個四年長的騙局。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：彈劾特朗普條款下周一交參院<br />\n<br />\nQAnon一些人卻提出新說法「補鑊」，如指美國現在實是由軍方而非拜登控制；拜登就職禮不合法，特朗普的「真就職禮」將在3月舉行；甚至特朗普和拜登換了臉等。專家指QAnon分化可能更危險，因為白人至上和新納粹團體，會嘗試將幻滅的QAnon追隨者吸納進他們的意識形態。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華盛頓郵報》"},{"pid":"9b8532946e02fd1c01b319d155a5225cf488e355","tid":2377112,"uid":19527,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"美國《華盛頓郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffd39baef6332623998638906f5dc99a27834df","tid":2377112,"uid":4783,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"蘋果繼續玩啦<br />\nunsub算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b371ad9eb1cfa822d8ceaa4b862480956fa8500","tid":2377112,"uid":158613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cffd39baef6332623998638906f5dc99a27834df","tid":2377112,"uid":4783,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"蘋果繼續玩啦<br />\nunsub算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"人哋係食老千貪腐集團條水<br />\n冇say<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf10b6ecf2a9fd346540afa26ad068f21ceaff83","tid":2377112,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b371ad9eb1cfa822d8ceaa4b862480956fa8500","tid":2377112,"uid":158613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cffd39baef6332623998638906f5dc99a27834df","tid":2377112,"uid":4783,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"蘋果繼續玩啦<br />\nunsub算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"人哋係食老千貪腐集團條水<br />\n冇say<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"諗住奶登條水喉<br />\n唔會志在你一千幾百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73105d95fecb6c5dc15ecf5dff3f679a1a98e39","tid":2377112,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T12:51:34.000Z","msg":"QAnon<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}